- Run `npm run build` or `tsc --noEmit` to ensure there are no TypeScript errors with the new Lucide icons or route configs.

### Manual Verification
- Code review of `App.tsx` and `_nav.ts` to ensure exact match with the "3-navigation-map.md" spec.
